Provenance, neutrality & governance
-------------------------------------
agentactioncapsule-web is the static website for agentactioncapsule.org — the
neutral standard site and documentation for the Agent Action Capsule, an open
profile on IETF SCITT for verifiable records of agent actions.

It is neutral substrate. The content is product-free: it carries no commercial,
monetization, or tiering language. It documents the open specification and the
open-source implementations, and is designed with a clean transfer path to a
neutral standards body or foundation when the ecosystem matures.

This site links to, but does not vendor, the implementation repositories
published under https://github.com/action-state-group (Apache-2.0).
